{"word":"G4184 - πολύσπλαγχνος - polýsplanchnos - pol-oo'-splankh-nos - Very pitiful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πολύσπλαγχνος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">polýsplanchnos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pol-oo'-splankh-nos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Very pitiful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மிகுந்த உருக்கமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"full of pity, very kind, very tender - hearted, extremely full of pity"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4183 - πολύς - polýs - pol-oos'/4183\">G4183</a> and <a href=\"#/G4698 - σπλάγχνον - splánchnon - splangkh'-non/4698\">G4698</a> (figuratively), <i>extremely compassionate:</i> - very pitiful.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2155/2155\">G2155</a>, <a href=\"#/G4184/4184\">G4184</a>, <a href=\"#/G4697/4697\">G4697</a>, <a href=\"#/G4698/4698\">G4698</a>"}]}